MANDATORY API CONTRACT — follow EXACTLY:

BATCHES: POST /v1/batches uses form-data NOT JSON: requests.post(url, data={'source_url':'...','count':'5'}). Response: {"batch":{"id":"uuid",...},"items":[...]}. batch_id path param must be valid UUID.

ASSETS: POST /v1/assets/upload (NOT /v1/assets). Multipart form. Required: file + kind (gameplay|music|font). Response: {"asset":{"id":"uuid","kind":"..."}}

AGENTS: POST /v1/agents/bootstrap no body. POST /v1/agents/webhooks/elevenlabs (PLURAL webhooks).

CHATS — THIS IS CRITICAL:
POST /v1/chats JSON body. Response is NESTED: {"chat":{"id":"uuid","title":"..."}}
chat_id = response.json()['chat']['id']
NEVER USE response.json()['chat_id'] — THAT KEY DOES NOT EXIST
GET /v1/chats: {"items":[{"id":"..."},...]}

ENGAGEMENT: POST /v1/chats/{chat_id}/engagement requires item_id, viewer_id, session_id (strings). Response: {"engagement":{"id":"..."}}

RECOMMENDATIONS: GET /v1/chats/{chat_id}/recommendations: {"has_enough_data":bool,...}

SSE: DO NOT import sseclient. Use response.iter_lines().

Server at http://localhost:8000.
